Please follow the following instructions to set up a GitHub account.
- First, [create an account](https://github.com/join) using your `@ons.gov.uk` account.
- Remember to set up [2-factor authencation](https://help.github.com/en/articles/securing-your-account-with-two-factor-authentication-2fa).
- Speak to a member of the Platform team to get the right permissions for editing the repo.
